question: List all known variants of the RARG gene.
cypher:
MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('RARG')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('RARG'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50

MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('ERBB4')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('ERBB4'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50

MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('PIK3CG')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('PIK3CG'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50

MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('PIK3R2')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('PIK3R2'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50

MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('HDAC5')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('HDAC5'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50

MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('FN1')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('FN1'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50

MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('NDUFB11')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('NDUFB11'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50
